title: Saddleback Mountain-Arizona Settlement Act of 1995
content: Saddleback Mountain-Arizona Settlement Act of 1995 - Approves and ratifies the Settlement Agreement providing for the transfer of certain lands in Scottsdale, Arizona, by the Resolution Trust Corporation to the Salt River Pima-Maricopa Indian Community and the City of Scottsdale. Directs the Corporation to make such land transfer. Sets forth land use limitations .
